(132, '_transient_dash_f69de0bbfe7eaa113146875f40c02000', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2016/01/wordpress-4-4-1-security-and-maintenance-release/''>WordPress 4.4.1 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">06.01.2016</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.4.1 is now available. This is a security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. WordPress versions 4.4 and earlier are affected by a cross-site scripting vulnerability that could allow a site to be compromised. This was reported by Crtc4L. There were also several non-security bug fixes: Emoji [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-4-5-development-kicks-off-release-set-for-mid-april''>WPTavern: WordPress 4.5 Development Kicks Off, Release Set for Mid-April</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/briar-a-free-minimalist-wordpress-theme-based-on-bootstrap''>WPTavern: Briar: A Free Minimalist WordPress Theme Based on Bootstrap</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-4-4-1-patches-xss-security-vulnerability''>WPTavern: WordPress 4.4.1 Patches XSS Security Vulnerability</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Популярный плагин:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Google Analytics Dashboard for WP</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp&amp;_wpnonce=b69c244ebe&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Google Analytics Dashboard for WP''>Установить</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
